        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This thick piece of leather decorated with purple threads makes an attractive necktie but also serves a functional purpose: protecting the neck from hits that you don\u2019t see coming. You gain a +1 circumstance bonus to AC against attacks while off-guard from flanking.",
